data.body:
com.badlogic.gdx.utils.LongMap.Keys should implement Iterable<Long> and Iterator<Long>, analog to com.badlogic.gdx.utils.LongMap.Values.

Right now this is possible:
for (SomeObject value: mLongMap.values()) {...}

But his is not:
for (Long key : mLongMap.keys()) {...}

This applies to all ...Map.Keys classes in com.badlogic.gdx.utils btw... But I refrained from creating seperate issue tasks for now.

https://github.com/libgdx/libgdx/issues/1155

Latest nightlies (20.01.2014) reintroduces the problem. See original issue for more details and code.

Additional information: The font in the original was created this way:

FreeTypeFontGenerator generator = new FreeTypeFontGenerator(Gdx.files.internal("fonts/DroidSans.ttf"));
BitmapFont mFont_Default24 = generator.generateFont(24);
generator.dispose();
